_json.description: Planning a Garden Raised Bed - For Anyone with Bent Problems  The raised garden bed is perfect for older or disabled gardeners as well as for anyone who doesn't like to do a lot of hard bending on the back.  The garden bed should be wide enough to grow the plants you want comfortably but narrow enough to easily reach the middle of both sides, especially if you plan to plant vegetables or flowers to cut or harvest.
